        "content": "<p>I just attended the third EOSC EDEN seminar entitled <a href=\"https://eden-fidelis.eu/events/deep-dive-requirements-analysis-specifications-registry-long-term-access-and-preservation\">Deep Dive on Requirements Analysis, Specifications &amp; Registry for long-term access and preservation services</a> couldn't help noticing <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"928678\">@Paul Boon</span> on a slide about FAIRiCat.</p>",
