        "sender_full_name": "Philip Durbin 🚀",
        "timestamp": 1775657832
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>T2.3: FAIRiCat Framework implementation Dataverse</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2026-04-08 at 8.48.11 AM.png\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"3098x2030\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/53090/TbJbIQhl__zOtUc8oWYWLcG0/Screenshot-2026-04-08-at-8.48.11AM.png\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/53090/TbJbIQhl__zOtUc8oWYWLcG0/Screenshot-2026-04-08-at-8.48.11AM.png/840x560.webp\"></p>",
