    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"928678\">@Paul Boon</span> I'd love to hear more about <a href=\"https://github.com/EOSC-EDEN/wp2-FAIRiCat-implementation\">https://github.com/EOSC-EDEN/wp2-FAIRiCat-implementation</a> ! <span aria-label=\"heart\" class=\"emoji emoji-2764\" role=\"img\" title=\"heart\">:heart:</span> </p>\n<p>I see that the README starts with this:</p>\n<p>\"While implementing FAIRiCat for our repositories (Dataverse archives at DANS) it became apparent that the way we solved some of the issues we encountered might be helpful for others that would need to implement FAIRiCat for their repositories.\"</p>",
